ent-AU14WYclothingequipmentvendor = We-Yu PMC apparel vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Weyland-Yutani PMC apparel. Standard issue aboard naval vessels, military outposts, corporate-science installations and civilian colonies across the frontier. Manufactured to outfit personnel rapidly following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For full operational readiness, select one item from each section: fatigues with a webbing, footwear, gloves, headgear, armor, backpack, belt and a pouch.
ent-AU14WYequipmentvendor = We-Yu PMC equipment vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Weyland-Yutani PMC equipment. Stocked with medical supplies and field gear for rapid deployment following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization. The interface is intentionally simple, even someone with tunnel-vision and frostbite can operate it.
        Rapid-issue protocol: prioritize medical supplies, a ration pack, an e-tool and sandbags.
ent-AU14WYcorpsmanvendor = We-Yu PMC medical vendor
    .desc =
        An automated medical rack, hooked up to a compact stock of Weyland-Yutani PMC trauma supplies. Standard issue for corpsmen aboard naval vessels, outposts and colonies where casualties arrive faster than reinforcements. Designed for rapid reconstitution of combat medics following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency call-up.
        Corpsman protocol: select the essential equipment set, storage and limited medications.
ent-AU14WYaircrewvendor = We-Yu PMC aircrew vendor
    .desc =
        An automated dispenser rack, hooked up to a small storage of Weyland-Yutani PMC aircrew flight and support gear. Engineered to get flight personnel flight-ready in seconds after cryogenic hypersleep or scramble orders.
        Aircrew protocol: select a set of fatigues, the essential medical equipment and storage kit.
ent-AU14WYdirectorequipmentvendor = We-Yu PMC command vendor
    .desc = An automated command rack, hooked up to a restricted storage of Weyland-Yutani PMC command-leadership equipment. Manufactured to equip commanding personnel following cryogenic hypersleep or an emergency directive is issued.
ent-AU14WYSGequipmentvendor = We-Yu PMC smartgunner equipment vendor
    .desc = An automated smartgunner rack, hooked up to a small armory of Weyland-Yutani PMC heavy-weapon operator systems. Standard issue for designated smart-gun crews on naval vessels and high-threat outposts. Built to bring heavy fire support online rapidly after cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
ent-AU14WYsupervisorequipmentvendor = We-Yu PMC supervisor vendor
    .desc = An automated supervisor rack, hooked up to a compact storage of Weyland-Yutani PMC supervising equipment. Designed for immediate readiness following cryogenic hypersleep or rapid mobilization orders.
ent-AU14WYWeaponsVendor = We-Yu PMC weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated weapons rack, hooked up to a small armory of Weyland-Yutani PMC weaponry. Standard issue across the frontier where threats can appear without warning. Engineered to arm personnel in seconds following cryogenic hypersleep or emergency mobilization.
        For immediate combat readiness: select a primary weapon kit and a sidearm.
ent-AU14WYSpecialWeaponsVendor = We-Yu PMC special weapons rack
    .desc =
        An automated special weapons rack, hooked up to a restricted armory of Weyland-Yutani PMC heavy and breaching ordnance. Standard issue only for qualified operators. Engineered to deliver overwhelming firepower the instant cryogenic hypersleep ends or an emergency mobilization is called.
        Special weapons protocol: one weapon system of choice with a full ammunition loadout and explosives.
ent-AU14WYPMCRequisitionVendor = We-Yu PMC automated requisitions vendor
    .desc = An automated supply rack hooked up to a big storage of various firearms, ammunitions, explosives, load carrying equipment and other miscellaneous items.
